New powers emerge<br>
-------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
<br>
I was walking through the halls of the casters guild in Neriak two days past when I first heard that Al Kabor was up to something. We all knew him as that little kid who tried to make himself stronger by increasing the area of effect of his spells. Little did he know that the lost a considerable amount of power in doing so. Needless to say the first 70 years of his life were not fun at all. But I have heard taht he was locking himself in the Libary as of late working on a new type of transportaton spell. Call me symplystic but we tear a hole is space and guide people through it. It is not that difficult a concept I dont know how you can change that. We shall see.<br>
<br>
**the next day**<br>
<br>
I finally found that fool. He is in there saying something about porting people to where thier essence is anchored on this plane. We can already do that one of the first spells we learned. Granted it isnt all that great but gate has helped us all. I have some of my watchers keeping an eye on him. I dont quite trust this one.<br>
<br>
well one of the ladies who brought him his lunch brought me a piece of parchment he was writing on. It appears he is trying to find a way to return others to thier point of anchoring. Now this is most interesting indeed. This can be a most valuable tool. There is also some scrible here of attempting to send them to one of the 4 corners of the world as well. This is even more interesting. Everyone growing up knew that upon the 4 continents ruled by the combine empire there existed a place of power where all the energies of transportation were focused into a spire.<br>
<br>
I will have to speak with him on this. I must know more of this power if he messes this one up we could have a whole open in the land that could contain nothing but a void. I will update this when I find him<br>
<br>
** this morning**<br>
<br>
I found him in the library and he had jsut finished scribing his first sets of the spells. Immediately I thought of turning tail but I am not a druid I dont run from a challange. So i was a test subjet he told me he was going to send me to the eastern spire in faydwer. Sure enough the portal opened. let me say I enjoyed just stitting back for once. sure as there is hair on a halfings back I wound up in the foul lad of the woodelfs. I immediately gated back home and was very excited to get these spells. Well as a rewared for being a test subject he gave me one of each of the spells he had. And after that i knoced him out cold for not telling me he hadnt tried them before. <br>
<br>
Well I will try these new toys out here shortly but I am going to put my hand back on this halfling meat cause it is taking the swelling down. Let you know how the first test of mine will go on the reaper.<br>
<br>
Vinar Ruinthang<br>
